      <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.8">
        <div>Version <strong style="color:var(--text)">1.6.0</strong></div>
        <div>Discord selfbot presence + quest automation panel</div>
        <div style="margin-top:8px;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--text-3)">All features run locally on your machine.<br>Keep your token private.</div>
